  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nfeature.\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\nHooks can only be used in functional component.\r\n\r\n**What is the expected behavior?**\r\nIs there a plan to enable the usage of the hooks in the class component?\r\n\r\nHi\r\nI know there are quite a few drawbacks for the class component and that is one of the motivations why the hook is introduced.\r\nAnd, the hook do seem to be very outstanding.\r\nHowever, due to the javascript proposal, a decorator can only be used in the class, which may indicate the conflict between the hook and the decorator.\r\nSo my question is that is that possible for developers to use the hook in the class component in the future ?\r\nOr is that possible to use the hook and the decorator at the same time in React.\r\n\r\nThanks",
